Al Ferguson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Al_Ferguson 0 Al Ferguson (19 April 1888 – 4 December 1971) was an Irish-born American film actor. He appeared in nearly 300 films between 1912 and 1956. He was born in County Wexford, Ireland and died in Burbank, California. He is interred at Glendale's Forest Lawn Memorial Park Cemetery.
